Package ohos.agp.graphics

Class TextureHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.graphics.TextureHolder

  • public class TextureHolder
extends Object
    Captures frames from an image stream as an texture.

    The image stream may come from either camera preview or video decode. A Surface created from a TextureHolder can be used as an output destination for the image stream.

    Since:
    3
